snippet.title: BullShoppe Trailer (Available Now)
snippet.description:
Our debut single-player frenzy game BullShoppe is now available on Itch.io! Our little team has been heads down on this for quite awhile and we're excited to share it with the world.

Available now on Itch.io!
https://catalyst-softworks.itch.io/bullshoppe

Throw us your email on our site for updates on the game!
https://catalystsoftworks.com/

We'll also be posting updates to our Twitter! Check us out there.
https://twitter.com/catalystsoft
